title: Weed Remover Tool Wire Brush Scraper Set with Metal Broom & Weed Removal Head - Remove Weed & Moss from Block Paving Garden Path Patio and Driveway Easily
features: PATIO CLEANING WEEDING TOOL BRUSH SET - Removing weeds has never been so easy. The block paving weeder is specially designed to remove stubborn weed and moss from your garden path and driveway.

DUAL POWER WEED KILLER & REMOVER - This set has 2 wire brush heads. One is an angled bristle weed remover brush, specially designed with angled wire bristles to fit between the gaps in your block paving and paths. The second is a wire broom head which is perfect for sweeping and cleaning moss from patios.

BLOCK PAVING WEED DESTROYER - You work hard to keep your garden looking its best. No matter what you try you always end up with weeds sneaking through the gaps! This weed removal set is designed to combat the issue and leave you coming out on top of the weeds!

TELESCOPIC METAL LONG HANDLE - No more bending or back ache from trying to manually pull weeds from your garden. The fully adjustable handle simply twists and locks into place. With a range from 80cm to 140cm just adjust to find the right height for you!

PATIO CLEANER WIRE BRUSH - The garden tool patio cleaner is the ultimate weed killer and remover from block paving and slabs. The weed puller and wire brush scraper also can remove moss and algae from your patio, driveway, block paving and slabs.
